* [[*user Woedenaz]]的[https://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/component:toggle-sidebar-bhl 黑标切换侧边栏]；
* [[*user Croquembouche]]的[https://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/component:croqstyle Croq风格CSS]；
